===Records set===
The following records were set in Super Bowl XV, according to the official NFL.com boxscore and the Pro-Football-Reference.com game summary.

* ‡ Sacks have been an official statistic since Super Bowl XVII by the NFL. Sacks are listed as &quot;Tackled Attempting to Pass&quot; in the official NFL box score for Super Bowl XV.




==Starting lineups==
