===Records set===
The following records were set in Super Bowl XXIV, according to the official NFL.com boxscore, the 2022 NFL Record &amp; Fact Book and the ProFootball reference.com game summary. &lt;br&gt;Some records have to meet NFL minimum number of attempts to be recognized. The minimums are shown (in parentheses).


Turnovers are defined as the number of times losing the ball on interceptions and fumbles.


This is also the first and only NFL game to end with a final score of 55–10, which is scorigami.

